## Collections Strategy

PH collections are highly visible curated lists. Creating collections = authority.

**Collections to create:** Build collections around pillars:
{{#each pillars}}
{{add1 @index}}. **{{name}}** → curate tools related to [{{join topics ", "}}]
{{/each}}

**Rules:**
- 8-12 products per collection (not just yours)
- Genuine descriptions for each product
- Your tools included naturally among others
- Update monthly

